data.description: LOCATION!!!LOCATION!!!LOCATION!!! WELCOME HOME!! To this Beautiful Corner lot One Story Energy Efficient Home which includes Solar Panels That will help you save on utilities bills. This Amazing Home features a Welcoming large formal Living and Dining Room great for gatherings, Amazing Kitchen with lot's of cabinet space. HUGE above ground pool, mature trees perfect for entertaining. The outdoor has a bonus room. Located on the East Side of San Antonio with easy access to HWY 410 South. Close to all of the hustle & bustle Minutes away from Numerous shopping centers. It's a MUST SEE!!!!!
